#: ../../making_first_map.rst:3
msgid "製作第一張地圖"
msgstr "Make Your First Map"

#: ../../making_first_map.rst:5
msgid ""
"說到 GMT 中最簡單的繪圖指令，那非 ``pscoast`` 莫屬。在本章中，我們要來解說如何用 ``pscoast`` 製作海岸線地圖、GMT"
" 本身的參數輸入風格，以及如何調整這些參數。"
msgstr ""
"The very first command in the beginning is definitely ``pscoast``, which is also the easiest command for mapping. "
"In this chapter, we're going to see how to make a map with coastlines using ``pscoast``. The other "
"topics in this chapter are the style of GMT input and how to set up these input parameters."

#: ../../making_first_map.rst:9
msgid "目標"
msgstr "Goal"

#: ../../making_first_map.rst:10
#, python-format
msgid ""
"製作一張\\ `群島海 <https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E7%BE%A4%E5%B2%9B%E6%B5%B7>`_"
" (Archipelago Sea) 的地圖，如下圖所示。群島海位於北歐，是波羅的海的一個附屬海，海如其\\ "
"名，被大小不等的眾多島嶼給佔據。事實上，群島海很有可能是擁有最多島嶼的海，雖然大部分的島\\ 都很小就是了。西邊的最大島嶼叫做奧蘭島 "
"(Åland)，屬於芬蘭下轄的自治區。這麼多島嶼的地方，\\ 用來觀察 ``pscoast`` 的各種調整效果再適合不過了。"
msgstr ""
"Make a map of `Archipelago Sea <https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Archipelago_Sea>`_, as the figure here shows. "
"Located in Northern Europe, Archipelago Sea is actually part of the Baltic Sea. "
"As its name suggests, the sea are actually occupied by numerous islands in any size. Although "
"Most islands are small, Archipelago Sea possibly contains the most island in the world. "
"The largest island in the archipelago is Åland, an autonomous region of Finland. Such a place makes itself "
"ideal to show how ``pscoast`` can fine tune your coasline map."

#: ../../making_first_map.rst:20
msgid "直接觀看\\ `指令稿`_"
msgstr "Go to the final `Script`_ "

